summaries.full: Kuba meets with Marek, a high-ranking police officer who helps him keep law enforcement at bay, but unfortunately, Marek has no good news for him. As Kuba begins to worry about what may come next, he tasks Stryj with collecting the ill-fated bag of drugs.
